OPPOSITE G. Peter Jemison.
51. Number One. 1980. Gouache,
crayon, metallic paint, and
pencil on printed brown paper bag
with a corn husk inside, 13% x
74% in. (35 x 18 x 10.5 cm)
Art Bag. 1980. Crayon, oil pas-
tel, fabric, rope, plastic tag,
jigsaw puzzle piece, and ticket

paper bag with three printed
metal pins and a business card
inside, 20 x 13 x 7 in. (50.8 *
33 x 17.8 cm)

Dialogues (1980)

Gouache, crayon, marker, pen,
colored pencil, and cut-and-

6 in. (49 x 29.8 × 17.2 cm)
Works contemporaneous with those
shown by Jemison in the exhibi-
tion Dialogues (1980)
